title: Avoid unnecessary List
body: I happened to see an IDE0306 on this line while looking at something else. It suggested using a collection initializer but `Process[]` is already `IEnumerable<Process>` so that's unnecessary.

commit.message:
Avoid unnecessary List

I happened to see an IDE0306 on this line while looking at something else. It suggested using a collection initializer but `Process[]` is already `IEnumerable<Process>` so that's unnecessary.
